headline: Kraft Heinz must face Mac & Cheese lawsuit, judge rules
summary: A federal judge said Kraft Heinz must face a proposed nationwide class action alleging that it defrauded consumers by claiming its Kraft macaroni and cheese, one of its best-known products, contains no artificial preservatives.
